1. List of data files
	Filename: Descriptive Statistics of Annual Temperature a from 1980 to 2012 across Stations
	Short description: Short description: Descriptive Statistics containing N, Range, Min, Max., Mean, Std. Deviation, Variance of annual precipitation across 8 statin in Nepal from year 1980 to 2012 

	Filename: District Descriptive Statistics of Temperature and Rainfall from 1980 to 2012
	Short description: Minimum, Maximum, Mean and Std. Deviationfor temperature and rainfall across Nepal 

